{"tid":1130354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★非港豬！】工作不開心 印傭擸磚傷僱主逃逸","createTime":"2019-04-29T03:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T05:12:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce8b4f21aa90a889853884c1282cacd608aebb77","tid":1130354,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"大埔汀角路船灣陳屋村一名姓陳(74歲)男子，於昨日(28日)晚上10時許報案，指因工作態度問題，與其印尼籍女傭(約30至40歲)在屋內發生爭執，繼而被對方用磚頭襲擊，女傭再毀壞村屋一道鐵閘後逃去無蹤。陳手部受傷，由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害及刑事毀壞，交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/bkn-20190429013354030-0429_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fbkn-20190429013354030-0429_00822_001.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9d6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=c8aaadb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/bkn-20190429013354030-0429_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3e0fabea3b23e1102e196ff5e49bc3b4976d712f","tid":1130354,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:42:20.000Z","msg":"如果發生在垃圾港豬身上，只會ifc"},{"pid":"d97c31c753415f9615165c47db5fa5743b173518","tid":1130354,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:03:17.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1204196567755b712c5f94f623625b974b25505a","tid":1130354,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"老貓你咪再唔聽教<br />\n<br />\n倒公司米<br />\n<br />\n講公司壞話"},{"pid":"3afd02a61f86a3a9bebd66181b827aba8081fde0","tid":1130354,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1204196567755b712c5f94f623625b974b25505a","tid":1130354,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"老貓你咪再唔聽教<br />\n<br />\n倒公司米<br />\n<br />\n講公司壞話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\